<li>Words cannot express how saddened I am by your loss.</li>
<li>Please accept my heartfelt condolences. Your family is in my thoughts and prayers.</li>
<li>Holding you and your family close in my heart.</li>
<li>May [Deceased's name]'s memory be a blessing to you all.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and peace during this time of sorrow.</li>
<li>Your family is in my thoughts. I'm here for you if you need anything at all.</li>
<li>With deepest sympathy, I offer my condolences to you and your family.</li>
<li>I'm so very sorry to hear about the passing of your beloved [Deceased's name].</li>
<li>May you find comfort in the love and support of those around you.</li>
<li>Cherish the memories you shared.  They will always remain.</li>
<li> Sending love and prayers for strength and healing.</li>
    

